                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940917-39-off197 t17940917-39-cd198"></join>, a coachman's box great coat, value 1l.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17940917-39-victim569" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
